{"tid":2100300,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"你會否參與「非法」的初選？","createTime":"2020-07-09T03:15:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T14:51:22.000Z","uid":324193,"like":45,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"c36001164411d21f028d17d107f98d0c93fe7a4e","tid":2100300,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T03:15:24.000Z","msg":"//曾國衞提醒組織活動的人士，《選舉(舞弊及非法行為)條例》內清楚列明選舉候選人的定義、選舉開支的規限等，除候選人本身及代理人外，其他人士在競選過程中產生選舉開支均屬違法，另條例亦有明確規定禁止在選舉期間進行某些活動等。他又指，<span class=\"red\"><strong>組織、策劃及參與初選活動，有可能違反《港區國安法》第20條、第22條及第29條，一旦干犯，屬於嚴重罪行。</strong></span>他又呼籲市民參與初選時不要聚集，以免違反「禁聚令」，增加衞生風險，同時要留意主辦單位對個人資料是否有足夠保障。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200709/mobile/bkn-20200709000121092-0709_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200709%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200709000121092-0709_00822_001.html&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmkbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=7dae4c5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200709/mobile/bkn-20200709000121092-0709_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">你會否參與「非法」的初選？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n//<span class=\"red\">初選是讓市民在國安法壓境下，選擇做順民還是暴民，初選勝利者的政治路線和主張，即代表未來的抗爭運動方向。</span>有民間組織在 7 月 4 日自發舉行九龍東地區初選論壇，參選者被問到「會否為大局簽名支持國安法？」，有人表示可能會簽，也有人表示堅決不簽。這條簡單的問題，剛好有兩點需要市民去想清楚。一是「什麼是大局？」，這點出市民想抗爭會得到什麼結果，是35+ 的議會還是重建香港制度的機會？兩者那一樣是手段（mean）？那一樣是目的（end）?二是關於「簽名」背後的抗爭模式。容筆者先引一段歷史，在二戰前的英法兩國一直對德國採取綏靖政策，容忍德國擴軍並吞併捷克斯洛伐克，最終到德國入侵波蘭，英法才被迫對德宣戰。那麼在 DQ 危機下香港人到底選擇綏靖還是對抗呢？//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%83%E5%8F%83%E5%8A%A0%E4%B8%80%E5%A0%B4-%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95-%E7%9A%84%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E5%97%8E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%258F%2583%25E5%258A%25A0%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E5%2597%258E%2F&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmkbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=c29f652b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%258F%2583%25E5%258A%25A0%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E5%2597%258E%2F&h=8ba2e6d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%83%E5%8F%83%E5%8A%A0%E4%B8%80%E5%A0%B4-%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95-%E7%9A%84%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E5%97%8E/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">香港人，約定你投票</span></span>"},{"pid":"c5172059942ab2b86829bb744a60b90fa1984bc3","tid":2100300,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T03:19:57.000Z","msg":"點解會違反《港區國安法》第20條、第22條及第29條？"},{"pid":"ab767ded4df26c474102e4d6c5fe1e0115b33fee","tid":2100300,"uid":295279,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T03:22:51.000Z","msg":"非法 不了，所以我參加 合法果個"},{"pid":"776ccab449f7586acce17cac9e7b78393e412fda","tid":2100300,"uid":320680,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"c5172059942ab2b86829bb744a60b90fa1984bc3","tid":2100300,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T03:19:57.000Z","msg":"點解會違反《港區國安法》第20條、第22條及第29條？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T03:26:31.000Z","msg":"冇點解，佢睇你唔順眼你就係違反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa364148b0197f6784c5985e86bc14fc2ee57b7","tid":2100300,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5172059942ab2b86829bb744a60b90fa1984bc3","tid":2100300,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T03:19:57.000Z","msg":"點解會違反《港區國安法》第20條、第22條及第29條？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T03:28:30.000Z","msg":"寫完都唔覺邊撚度有違反<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U4zQ3qq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU4zQ3qq.png&h=3fe08a5d&